♪Life is but a fleeting play♪

59
00:09:12,068 --> 00:09:17,760
♪Exposed plot in the tapestry of fate♪

60
00:09:18,468 --> 00:09:24,224
♪A thousand threads
in a gamble of life and death♪

61
00:09:24,964 --> 00:09:30,720
♪Reluctance and hesitation,
as wavering shadows of a lamp♪

62
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:36,832
♪Breeze brings a whole night of rain♪

63
00:09:37,696 --> 00:09:43,616
♪From afar, I've drawn you on a scroll♪

64
00:09:44,128 --> 00:09:49,504
♪The inkstone,
finely carved with delicacy♪

65
00:09:50,336 --> 00:09:56,256
♪Love ignited, hair parted from comb♪

66
00:09:56,832 --> 00:10:02,912
♪The writer can never escape the pain♪

67
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:21,160
Rest well.

68
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,040
I'm sorry.

69
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:36,400
What?

70
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,320
Can I ask you something?

71
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,080
Yes?

72
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:47,680
That scar on your shoulder...

73
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:57,000
I've had it since I was a child.
What about it?

74
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:01,720
(She must have forgotten
that she once saved me.)

75
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:04,560
It's nothing...

76
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:41,480
(Young Lu Huai was saved by Su Luoluo.)

77
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:54,840
(Su Luoluo is Lu Huai's fetter.)

78
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:10,680
Now, it's me.

79
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:17,640
(Not only did you
ruthlessly scar yourself)

80
00:12:17,640 --> 00:12:19,680
(to steal Su Luoluo's story,)

81
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:25,120
(but you also feigned a loss of chastity
to fill Lu Huai with guilt.)

82
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:28,080
(Indeed, you are malicious at heart.)

83
00:12:35,640 --> 00:12:37,560
(What have you done to him?)

84
00:12:37,560 --> 00:12:38,784
I gave him some sedatives.

85
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:41,720
I knew you wouldn't
let anything happen to Su Luoluo.

86
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:43,136
It would be mostly to deal with me.

87
00:12:43,780 --> 00:12:44,676
So I was prepared.

